---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="404 — NosDicenGeeks"
  description="Esta página no existe. Quizás fue borrada, movida o nunca existió en esta realidad."
>
  <section class="error-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="terminal-window">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="terminal-dot dot--red"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot dot--green"></span>
          <span class="terminal-title">bash — nosdicengeeks</span>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-body">
          <p class="terminal-line">
            <span class="t-prompt">nosdicengeeks@blog:~$</span>
            <span class="t-cmd"> curl -s http://dev.nosdicengeeks.com{Astro.url.pathname}</span>
          </p>

          <div class="terminal-output">
            <p class="t-error">HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found</p>
            <p class="t-key">Content-Type: <span class="t-val">text/html; charset=utf-8</span></p>
            <p class="t-key">X-Error: <span class="t-val">Page not found in the matrix</span></p>
            <p class="t-key">X-Suggestion: <span class="t-val">Have you tried turning it off and on again?</span></p>
          </div>

          <div class="error-code" aria-label="Error 404">
            <span class="error-digit">4</span>
            <span class="error-digit error-digit--accent">0</span>
            <span class="error-digit">4</span>
          </div>

          <p class="error-message">
            <span class="t-comment">// </span>Esta página no existe en ningún namespace conocido.
          </p>
          <p class="error-submessage">
            Fue eliminada, movida o nunca existió en esta dimensión del stack.
          </p>

          <p class="terminal-line terminal-line--blink">
            <span class="t-prompt">nosdicengeeks@blog:~$</span>
            <span class="cursor" aria-hidden="true">█</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn--primary">cd ~/ → Volver al inicio</a>
        <a href="/posts" class="btn btn--outline">ls posts/ → Ver posts</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .error-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: calc(100vh - var(--header-height) - 120px);
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
  }

  .terminal-window {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card), 0 0 40px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.06);
  }

  .terminal-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .terminal-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot--red    { background: #FF5F57; }
  .dot--yellow { background: #FEBC2E; }
  .dot--green  { background: #28C840; }

  .terminal-title {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
    margin-right: 52px; /* offset the dots */
  }

  .terminal-body {
    background: var(--color-bg-code);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .terminal-line {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .t-prompt { color: var(--color-green); }
  .t-cmd    { color: var(--color-text-muted); }

  .terminal-output {
    margin-block: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .t-error { color: var(--color-danger); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: var(--space-1); }
  .t-key   { color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .t-val   { color: var(--color-yellow); }
  .t-comment { color: var(--color-green-dim); }

  /* Big 404 number */
  .error-code {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-block: var(--space-6);
  }

  .error-digit {
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 7rem);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
    line-height: 1;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  .error-digit--accent {
    color: var(--color-green);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-green);
  }

  .error-message {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .error-submessage {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Blinking cursor */
  .cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-green);
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50%       { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .error-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
